name: Stable Diffusion Web UI
short_desc: Powerful AI image generation with Automatic1111's Web UI.
description: Stable Diffusion Web UI allows you to generate high-quality images from text prompts (text-to-image) and image prompts (image-to-image) using various Stable Diffusion models. This Runtipi app provides a convenient way to host and manage the Automatic1111 Web UI on your server, leveraging your GPU for fast image generation.
author: Alastor Decidit Ripley
